<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>나의 다이어리 - Small Joys</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/register.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/home.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header class="header">
        <div class="logo">Small Joys</div>
        <nav class="nav">
            <a href="/shared">공유페이지</a>|
            <a href="/home" style="font-weight: bold; color: #5a9dc5;">나의 다이어리</a>|
            <a href="happy-find">행복찾기</a>|
            <a href="/mypage">마이페이지</a>|
            <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="diary-container">
        <div class="diary-header">
            <h2>나의 행복 일기 📝</h2>
            <a href="/post/new" class="new-post-btn">새 일기 쓰기 +</a>
        </div>

        <div class="diary-list">
            
            <% if (posts.length > 0) { %>
                <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
                    <a href="/post/detail/<%= post._id %>" class="diary-item">
                        <div class="item-info">
                            <h3><%= post.title %></h3>
                            <p><%= post.createdAt.toLocaleDateString('ko-KR') %></p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="item-status">
                            <% if (post.isPublic) { %>
                                <span class="status-public">🌏 공개</span>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <span class="status-private">🔒 비공개</span>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="no-posts">
                    <p>아직 작성한 일기가 없네요.</p>
                    <p>오늘의 소소한 행복을 기록해 보는 건 어떨까요?</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
         KAYWON UNIVERSITY DIGITAL MEDIA DESIGN JOOJAEHOON
         copyrtghtⓒJOOJAEHOON All RIGHT RESERVED | &copy; 2025
    </footer>

</body>
</html>